Linear Regression:¶

In [164]:
L <- lm(y.train ~ X.train)
yhat <- (cbind(1, X.test) %*% L$coef) >= 0.5
L.error <- mean(yhat != y.test)

KNN:¶

In [165]:
library(class)
k <- c(1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15)
k.error <- rep(NA, length(k))
for (i in 1:length(k)) {
    yhat <- knn(X.train, X.test, y.train, k[i])
    k.error[i] <- mean(yhat != y.test)
}
